Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.76,0:00:04.40,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Alibis, codes, tricks, deals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:06.35,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The mysterious Black Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.35,0:00:08.03,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A big case on the eve of a wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.03,0:00:09.95,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The lovers are closer than they seem!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:11.56,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.56,0:00:13.50,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:15.76,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.89,0:01:41.27,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}While showing Tokyo to Heiji and Kazuha,\Nwho had come to attend the wedding of a friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:43.59,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}we met with Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10},
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.59,0:01:46.54,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the butler of the family who were celebrating the marriage, the Morizonos.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.57,0:01:51.09,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He invited us to go to the Morizonos' mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:57.67,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That very evening, Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10}\Nwas murdered in a locked room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.67,0:02:02.99,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Kazuha found something in common\Nbetween two of the suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:15.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You can't find the weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.89,0:02:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've searched the house and grounds, but we've found nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, search again! It's got to be lying around somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.14,0:02:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got to find the weapon that killed Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.82,0:02:31.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not just the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:35.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may also find the murderer's bloodstained clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.04,0:02:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at Shigematsu-{\i1}han{\i0}'s body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:40.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's covered in blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:45.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the killer pulled the knife out,\Nblood must've spattered everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.44,0:02:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the murderer could've just been some random burglar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:56.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the butler saw him,\Nso the thief stabbed him and ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The house's security system is perfect,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:04.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the only outsiders who have entered recently
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:07.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,are us, the police, and the reporters,\Nwho showed up after the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And don't forget that the doors\Nand windows were locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A random thief couldn't have\Ngotten in and out so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer's gotta be somebody who knows\Nthis house and doesn't have an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:27.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That leaves just five people!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You questioned those people,\Ndidn't ya, Inspector? How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:32.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:34.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mikio, the master of the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,claims to have been in his room\Nwaiting for Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were planning to have a talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their daughter, Yurie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Nwas by herself, taking a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kikuhito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the son, was in his room\Nreading a magazine and listening to music.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:50.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the servant,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:53.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was looking around the house for the cat, as he'd been ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaede{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the fiancée,\Ntold a story that sounds a little fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.57,0:03:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She says she was taking a nap in her room\Nwhile she waited for her parents to pick her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fishy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:07.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems Yurie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} knocked on her door\Nto ask if she'd like to join her in the bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but she never got a reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.29,0:04:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, what happened to that window?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard there was a scuffle\Nafter the body was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kikuhito made some rude remarks,\Nso Sakuraba fed him a knuckle sandwich!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:28.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He punched him so hard, Kikuhito crashed into that window!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure! Could you come here for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:33.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Tome{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:35.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the bottom of this latch,\Nthere's a small blood stain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:46.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer must've touched it\Nwith blood-stained gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the killer opened and closed this window after the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The window was locked from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:57.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hattori.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this piece of broken glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:03.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a little hole in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.22,0:05:05.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoa. I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:08.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't notice it when I checked out the window before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:11.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't blame you for overlooking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from the shape of this broken piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:17.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the hole was right on the edge of the windowpane, where it was barely visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:20.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means we know what to look for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:23.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It should be somewhere on this balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, may I have a word?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was our butler,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.74,0:05:37.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but also a dear friend to my wife and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would like to hold a funeral as soon as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and bury him near my wife's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's what she would have wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I can't let you do anything until we're finished with the autopsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:06:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like that story my mom told me is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Story?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wife who died four years ago was actually in love with Shigematsu-{\i1}han{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She started dropping by this house to see Shigematsu-{\i1}han{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.46,0:06:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the man of the house thought she was coming to see him instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:17.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, he proposed to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The parents of both families hit it off really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She once told my mom that she was overwhelmed by his courtship and gave in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wife and the butler, huh? Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup. Sounds like the same old story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at those two, wearing the same pendant...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:41.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So have you been able to find it, Hattori?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:43.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope, nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if the killer escaped from the balcony, it's gotta be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:52.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's give it a try using the next balcony over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give what a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:07:00.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to find out if this escape method is really possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:02.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And who's gonna do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who else but you, Heiji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep your eye on the rope, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:23.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! How's it coming, Hattori?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a lot easier than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the murderer escaped downstairs from this balcony...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something stuck in that tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That tree, in front of the room with the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.88,0:07:47.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang on, Kudo! I'll be there in a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! Ain't that Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:54.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:07:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:01.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:03.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've gotta help that kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:05.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Help him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.95,0:08:21.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:23.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was {\i1}that{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kid was about to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Why didn't ya help him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were right there, weren't ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:36.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't blame him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:40.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kikuhito's been terrified of heights\Never since he was small.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:44.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... Come to think of it,\NShigematsu-{\i1}han{\i0} mentioned that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori, that thing you saw up in the tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let's go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! What're you two doing now?! Climbing trees?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:08:57.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:08:58.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A blood-stained shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:05.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a pair of gloves with blood on them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and a kitchen knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just as we suspected. Look, a piece of cellophane tape at the end of the string!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:18.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now we know who the killer is,\Nand how the room was locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,- Case closed!\N- Case closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, this feels wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. There's a bunch of questions\Nthat still ain't been answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:33.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really coming down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, it started to rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rain, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:38.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rain shutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.53,0:09:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aha! Now I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It makes sense now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:50.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The missin' weapon from the scene of the crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the blood marks on the floor\Nfrom the body bein' dragged,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the light turned off in the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:58.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the cat in the same room as the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the evidence tied up in a neat little bundle,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it all makes perfect sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:08.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's who the killer is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what're we gonna do? We've got no proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.82,0:10:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we can't find the proof...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:17.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll make the killer hand it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kazuha! Tell everybody to gather in the room with the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.83,0:10:27.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, can you ask the Inspector to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji-{\i1}niichan{\i0}'s got something important to tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You betcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this about? Calling us all here suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep y'all waitin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, now. What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not thinking of putting on a deduction show for us, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what I'm gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:52.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.39,0:10:57.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We figured out the locked-room trick, the killer, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:11:03.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup. The person who stabbed Shigematsu-{\i1}han{\i0} to death, locked the room and escaped from it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:05.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}... I'm talking about {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:09.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He {\i1}can't{\i0} be the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:12.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:15.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how'd he create the locked room?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you explain that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You betcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.51,0:11:27.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The key is to make a small hole in the glass of the window behind the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:28.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:32.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lab team has already checked that, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:34.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just take a look, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:38.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, I stick the loop onto the latch\Nwith some cellophane tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I put the broken piece of glass back into the windowpane and run the string through the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, I get out onto the balcony and close the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:56.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I just pull the string gently...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.16,0:12:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, I pull the string a little harder,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:06.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,making the string slip off the tape,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:08.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and pull it out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now we've got ourselves a locked-room murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:14.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:16.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if the police found it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:19.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} punched Kikuhito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted to hide the hole in the window by shattering the glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he punched him because\NKikuhito was being so rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:32.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just an excuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:36.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the start Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was lookin'\Nfor an opportunity to break the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But unluckily for him, the window didn't\Nbreak too neatly. The hole's still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't prove he's the murderer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:47.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think again, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.47,0:12:49.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murderer escaped from that balcony!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You couldn't possibly do it,\Nsince you've got a bad leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:57.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Neither could Kaede{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} or Yurie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:13:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kikuhito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s out of the question\Nsince he's afraid of heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That leaves one person, a guy nimble enough to get a cat out of the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you're the only one capable of doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:16.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You stabbed Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Nused that trick to lock the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then escaped downstairs from the balcony!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:22.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you came back up here,\Npretendin' you knew nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well? Am I wrong, Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:27.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:29.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:31.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't kill anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:34.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} can't be the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before he ran up here with everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was with {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:14:01.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! We were looking around the house for the cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why didn't you tell us that in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:09.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't want the others to know\Nabout your relationship, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:14.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two are wearin' the same pendant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must've bought it together somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:21.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. You two are lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You killed Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} because\Nhe thwarted your relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:28.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,by arranging her marriage to\Nsomeone else with the master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:30.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! I didn't kill anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's talk back at the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:36.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! We really were together the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.69,0:14:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but a testimony from someone who's intimate with the suspect isn't much evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:47.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.49,0:14:48.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No! It wasn't me! Please believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}... Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, dry your tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to wait forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:10.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,until that man disappears from your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I can't believe he killed Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:19.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:24.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's nothing but a monster in human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who else would kill kindly old Shigematsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:30.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure he'll accept his fate
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:37.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,once the murder weapon is discovered among his belongings or somethin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? You haven't found the weapon yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's it for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be back again tomorrow to look for the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:51.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess we'll be heading out, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:55.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's already late, so let's spend the night here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:15:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:28.15,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Sakuraba"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it was you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:47.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kikuhito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:52.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You thought you could get away with it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:56.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,by leaving all that fake evidence against Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.19,0:16:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but you can't deceive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:00.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:03.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have done it! I'm afraid of heights!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That whole trick was a bluff!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:09.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You left the bloodstain on the window latch on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were no traces of blood on the balcony!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:15.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After leaving that one stain,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:19.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why would the killer suddenly take off his bloody gloves to climb down the balcony?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:23.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-So what trick {\i1}did{\i0} I use to get out of the locked room?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.55,0:17:25.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was no trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:29.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were in that room the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:33.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were probably hiding behind a curtain
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in the corner of the room next to the room where the body was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:39.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you closed one of the rain shutters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So nobody outside would see you hiding behind the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You prepared the taped string with the loop at the end and drilled the hole in the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you called Shigematsu-{\i1}han{\i0} into the room and stabbed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blood spattered on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:00.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but you were wearing one of Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s shirts, which you'd stolen in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You dragged his body into the room next door,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,wrapped the gloves and weapon in that shirt,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and threw it out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:12.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you saw us outside the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:15.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you broke the glass with the chair,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and hid behind the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, after we broke down the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we'd follow the blood into the next room and discover the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was pretty easy for you to come out from behind the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.89,0:18:34.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the room was dark and everyone was focused on the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.41,0:18:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,nobody saw you, so you were able to mingle yourself among everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as if you'd just heard the yell and came to see what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shut the cat in the room to make sure Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} didn't have a solid alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:50.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You knew that when the cat went missing, he'd be told to go look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But anyone could have done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.71,0:18:55.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, only you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:19:00.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fact that all the evidence was bundled up with string proves it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ordinarily, no criminal would just package up the evidence and throw it all away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:08.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of your fear of heights, you couldn't go out on the balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had to use the murder weapon as a weight to throw the clothes away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:17.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You goaded Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} into a fight so you could break the window with the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But by tricking Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} into punching you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you could make it seem like he broke the window on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:29.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came here to look for the weapon myself, to help with the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:32.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just found this knife in his bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah? Take a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That bag ain't Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:38.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's {\i1}mine{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room is really next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.19,0:19:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The room, the bag, the weapon you found in the bushes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.45,0:19:52.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the whole racket about Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s arrest...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it was all a trap we created with the Inspector's help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:58.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We knew you'd lower your guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:20:01.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and hand us the solid evidence on a platter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's all his fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:10.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He threatened to tell my father about my company's misdeeds
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:14.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,unless I called off the marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:19.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't get it. He was the one who set up the marriage in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:23.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if I cancelled the marriage,\NI was afraid he'd go on blackmailing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I decided to incriminate that guy who stole my fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He never stole anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:34.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaede{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was in love with Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shigematsu-{\i1}han{\i0} must've thought\Nshe was droppin' by to see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:40.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he pushed for the marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.64,0:20:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... He never said anything about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:47.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably didn't want to hurt your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, he was the one\Nwho suggested the marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm sure Shigematsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nnever wanted to blackmail you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.86,0:20:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He just wanted to stop the marriage
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:21:01.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so that two people who loved\Neach other could be together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:07.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, he'd been in the\Nsame situation once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.94,0:22:41.44,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tokyo Station
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.45,0:22:40.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.14,0:22:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just consider it payback for\Nthe time you helped us in Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.20,0:22:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you pulled off that\Ntrick without letting me in on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ya know how the sayin' goes. "To fool your enemies, you must fool your friends first..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.14,0:22:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, how are Sakuraba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Kaede{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just saw them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.50,0:23:00.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I apologized for\Ntreating him like a murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.77,0:23:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what's takin' Kazuha so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:07.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! Let me off the hook!\NI'm gonna die of embarrassment!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.36,0:23:10.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too late to complain!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:14.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kazuha, you're wearin' a striped shirt too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.25,0:23:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's not like that! This is Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:20.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For some reason, she forced me to wear it, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.28,0:23:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna change in the john!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.01,0:23:24.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mind you wearin' that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.35,0:23:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y'know, we kinda look like...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.02,0:23:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,L-Look like...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like brother and sister, dontcha think?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.99,0:23:41.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Rather than brother and sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:42.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}more like a comedy duo...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.27,0:24:07.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.61,0:24:15.62,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.62,0:24:20.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Photo of a star
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.49,0:24:22.88,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, a starry night!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.88,0:24:24.88,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, get my net!
